# Project Auto-Registration
# List enabled projects (one per line)
# Supports both flat and nested structures:
#   - Flat: <project-name>
#   - Nested: <category>/<project-name>
# Projects with :dev suffix are auto-built in dev mode
#
# Format: <project-path> or <project-path>:dev
# Example: games/cs-pathway:dev

# === NESTED STRUCTURE (organized by category) ===
# Games
games/cs-pathway:dev
games/gamify:dev

# Systems
#systems/student-management-groups

# === FLAT STRUCTURE (legacy/uncategorized) ===